                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 15.979%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #c9c9c9;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-color: #ffffff;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-top-width: 3px;border-top-style: Solid;border-top-color: #ffffff;" bgcolor="#C9C9C9" width="15.979%">
                    <p style="font-weight: bold;">Purpose</p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 84.021%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-top-width: 3px;border-top-color: #ffffff;border-top-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="84.021%">
                    <p style="color: #000000;">Creates a list of alarm variables that generate an action when triggered.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 15.979%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #c9c9c9;border-left-color: #ffffff;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#C9C9C9" width="15.979%">
                    <p style="font-weight: bold;">Description</p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 84.021%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="84.021%">
                    <p style="color: #000000;"><span>An alarm condition is triggered when:</span>
                    </p>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li style="color: #000000;" class="p" value="1">
                            <p style="color: #000000;">an alarm variable on any device is triggered</p>
                        </li>
                        <li style="color: #000000;" class="p" value="2">
                            <p style="color: #000000;">one or more alarm variables on different devices are triggered</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 15.979%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #c9c9c9;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-color: #ffffff;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#C9C9C9" width="15.979%">
                    <p style="font-weight: bold;">What to do first</p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 84.021%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="84.021%">
                    <p style="color: #000000;">Enable device alarm variables (see chapter <a href="Config-dispositivo__variabili_di_allarme.htm">Device setup: alarm variables</a>).</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
