        <p>&#160;</p>
        <table style="border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;width: 100%;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="100%" bgcolor="#C0C0C0">
            <col style="width: 6.856%;" />
            <col style="width: 93.144%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.856%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.856%">
                    <p class="Note">
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/AAwarning.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.144%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.144%">
                    <p style="color: #000000;font-weight: normal;">The system checks for alarms every 30 seconds. This interval is added to the delay set in the <a href="Attivita__regole_di_attivazione.htm" style="font-weight: bold;">Rules</a> page. Alarms cleared before the end of the delay +30 seconds are ignored.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
