                <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                    <li class="p" value="1">
                        <p>Enter the name of the alarm condition (i.e.:"No bank communications")</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="p" value="2">
                        <p>Select the device and alarm variable to be checked</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="p" value="3">
                        <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/dbllistbox/arrowdx_on.png" style="border: none;float: none;width: 54px;height: 19px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="54" height="19" border="0" /> to add the variable</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="p" value="4">
                        <p>Repeat to add as many variables to be checked as needed</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="p" value="5">
                        <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/add_on_26x25.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;width: 26;height: 25;" border="0" /></p>
